value.name: 43 (number) - Wikipedia
value.snippet: 43 is the largest prime which divides the order of the Janko group J 4. 43 is a repdigit in base 6 (111). 43 is the number of triangles inside the Sri Yantra. 43 is the largest natural number that is not an (original) McNugget number. 43 is the smallest prime number expressible as the sum of 2, 3, 4, or 5 different primes: 43 = 41 + 2; 43 = 11 + 13 + 19
